lib-5-6-1                     Xerox Quintus Prolog Library Manual                         Section 5-6-1: library(ask)ask_file(+Prompt, -FileName)            Reads FileName from the terminal, having prompted for it with            Prompt.  It continues prompting until a FileName is read for which            can_open_file(FileName, read, warn) is true, or until an empty line            is typed (in the latter case it fails quietly).ask_file(+Prompt, +Mode, -FileName)            Reads FileName from the terminal, having prompted for it with            Prompt.  It continues prompting until a FileName is read for which            can_open_file(FileName, Mode, warn) is true, or until an empty line            is typed (in the latter case it fails quietly).